name: ArcApps LC Pipeline Summary
query:
SELECT
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.name as "ID:Link/ArcApps LC Pipeline:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.brand as "Brand:Data/Brand:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.supplier_name as "Supplier Name:Data/Supplier Name:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.actual_pi_no as "Actual PI No:Data/Actual PI No:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.actual_pi_date as "Actual PI Date:Date/Actual PI Date:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.actual_pi_value as "Actual PI Value:Currency/Actual PI Value:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.actual_pi_currency as "Actual PI Currency:Select/Actual PI Currency:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.container_size as "Container Size:Data/Container Size:150",
	`tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.final_destination as "Final Destination:Currency/Final Destination:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.eta as "ETA:Date/ETA:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.ci_value as "CI Value:Currency/CI Value:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.etr as "ETR:Date/ETR:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.shipment_mode as "Shipment Mode:Select/Shipment Mode:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.shipment_status as "Shipment Status:Data/Shipment Status:150",
    `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`.pipeline_status as "Pipeline Status:Select/Pipeline Status:150"

FROM
  `tabArcApps LC Pipeline`
